text: I consider myself to be a reasonable consumer with reasonable expectations from those that I purchase from. Anymore, most companies no matter what their business are mediocre at best. No so with NorthShore Care Supply, they meet and/or exceed your expectations. Every time! Thank you, NorthShore for your high quality products and customer service.
